&lt;li&gt;Partner with peers in Model Risk Management and Fair Lending on second line teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and present portfolio risk analyses, monitoring results, and recommendations to senior leadership, governance committees, and other stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
